[Black "Chapter 10 Finegold Defense"]

{In this chapter, Black defers ...Nc6, retaining the option of ...Nbd7. The mainline continues 8... Be7 (the Finegold Defense), while 8... b5 leads to the Chicago Defense, typically followed by the ...Ra7 rook lift.}

1. e4 c5 2. d4 cxd4 3. c3 dxc3 4. Nxc3 d6 5. Nf3 e6 6. Bc4 a6 7. O-O Nf6 8. Qe2 {[%entry]} Be7 (8... b5 9. Bb3 Ra7 10. e5 (10. Rd1?! Rd7) 10... dxe5 11. Nxe5) 9. Rd1 Nbd7 10. e5 dxe5 11. Nxe5 O-O 12. Bf4 *

